%h1
  List of products (
  = @products.count
  )


- @products.each do |product|
  %p
    = product.name
    %b
      as sold by:
    = product.user.name
    = link_to 'Show', product
    = link_to 'Edit', edit_product_path(product)
    = link_to 'Delete', product, method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure?" }